```
init(
```

## [ Parameters ](/documentation/corenfc/nfciso15693customcommandconfiguration/init(manufacturercode:customcommandcode:requestparameters:)#parameters)

`manufacturerCode`8 bits manufacturer code.

`customCommandCode`8 bits custom command code. Valid range is 0xA0 to 0xDF.

`requestParameters`Optional custom request parameters.

## [Discussion](/documentation/corenfc/nfciso15693customcommandconfiguration/init(manufacturercode:customcommandcode:requestparameters:)#discussion)

Initialize with default zero maximum retry and zero retry interval.
